# Important point:

# Python dict la:

# quotes single or double irukkalaam
# bool = True
# None = None

# JSON la:

# keys and strings double quotes தான்
# bool = true
# null = null

# Example:

# Python dict:

# {"name": "food", "paid": True, "note": None}

# JSON:

# {"name":"food","paid":true,"note":null}

# So dictionary JSON ஆக மாறும்போது formatting and types convert aagum.